## SEO Agency vs Independent SEO Consultant — The Honest Comparison

Understanding the difference helps Reading businesses make better decisions about where to invest SEO budget:

**Traditional SEO agency model:**
- Multiple staff handling your account across strategy, content, and technical
- Account manager as your primary contact (not the strategist)
- Junior team members often execute day-to-day work
- Overhead costs built into pricing (office, management, support staff)
- Reporting through dashboards rather than strategic conversations

**Independent SEO consultant model:**
- One senior expert handling strategy, oversight, and execution
- Direct access to the person making every decision
- No account manager layer between you and the work
- Lower overhead translates to either lower cost or deeper scope for the same investment
- Strategic partnership rather than service-delivery relationship

For most Reading businesses — particularly professional services, technology, and growth-stage companies — the independent model delivers equivalent or better results at lower or similar investment. The person you speak to on a strategy call is the person building your topical maps, reviewing your technical audit, and writing your content briefs.

