## How Much Does a Reading SEO Agency Cost vs a Consultant?

Reading SEO agency pricing typically runs £1,500–£5,000+/month for mid-tier agencies, with larger agencies charging £3,000–£10,000+/month. Independent consultant pricing for equivalent strategic scope typically runs:

-   [Technical SEO audits](/services/technical-seo-audit): £500–£1,200
-   [Topical maps](/services/topical-maps): £800–£2,500+
-   Monthly retainers: £1,500–£5,000+ (dependent on scope, not headcount)

The key difference: agency pricing often reflects overhead and team structure rather than strategic value delivered to your business. Learn more about [SEO cost structures](/services/how-much-does-seo-cost) across different service models.

