## How Long Does SEO Take With a Reading Agency or Consultant?

Timelines are consistent whether you work with an agency or independent consultant — the work required is the same:

**Local SEO improvements** — initial results visible within 3-6 months through Google Business Profile optimisation and location-intent content.

**Topical authority building** — 6-12 months for competitive Reading markets, establishing comprehensive topic coverage that compounds over time.

**Technical SEO fixes** — often show measurable crawling and indexing improvements within 4-8 weeks of implementation.

The agency myth is that more people means faster results. In practice, SEO pace is limited by Google's crawl and re-evaluation cycles, not by headcount. Learn more about [realistic SEO timelines](/blog/how-long-does-seo-take).

